sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway<br/>(Istio/agentgateway/GKE)<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as llm-d-inference-scheduler<br/>(EPP)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant Prefill as Prefill vLLM<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Sidecar as routing-sidecar<br/>(decode pod)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Decode as Decode vLLM<br/>8200/TCP HTTP
    participant NIXL as NIXL KV Transfer<br/>5600/TCP RDMA/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OTEL as OTEL Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,Decode: Flow 1: Standard Inference (Optimized Baseline)
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80 (no auth)
    GW->>EPP: ext_proc gRPC/9002<br/>(scoring, filtering)
    EPP-->>GW: Selected backend
    GW->>Decode: HTTP/8000<br/>(direct to model server)
    Decode-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTP/80

    Note over Client,NIXL: Flow 2: Prefill/Decode Disaggregation
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    GW->>EPP: ext_proc gRPC/9002<br/>(prefill profile)
    EPP-->>GW: Selected prefill instance
    GW->>Prefill: HTTP/8000<br/>(prefill request)
    Prefill->>NIXL: KV cache transfer<br/>5600/TCP RDMA/TCP (L2, no encryption)
    NIXL->>Decode: KV cache data<br/>5600/TCP
    Sidecar->>Decode: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8200 (internal)
    Decode-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTP/80 via Gateway

    Note over Client,NIXL: Flow 3: Wide Expert-Parallelism (Multi-Node)
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    GW->>EPP: ext_proc gRPC/9002
    EPP-->>GW: Selected leader pod
    GW->>Sidecar: HTTP/8000<br/>(to leader pod)
    Sidecar->>Decode: Forward to leader vLLM
    Decode->>Decode: Worker RPC 5555/TCP<br/>(data parallel)
    Decode->>NIXL: NVSHMEM/NCCL collective<br/>IB/RoCE RDMA (L2)
    Decode-->>Client: Streamed response

    Note over Prefill,OTEL: Observability & Model Loading
    Prefill->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 (HF_TOKEN)
    Decode->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 (HF_TOKEN)
    Prefill->>OTEL: Traces<br/>OTLP gRPC/4317
    Decode->>OTEL: Traces<br/>OTLP gRPC/4317
    Prom->>Prefill: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8000
    Prom->>Decode: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8000
    Prom->>EPP: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/9002
